Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.78,0:02:49.75,op-cn-2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\pos(584,673)}镇魂歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:54.99,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只因太阳尚未西沉
